{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/ost-anime-yuri-ice-diputar-saat-winter-olympic-games-di-pyeongchang-korea-selatan/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"OST Anime Yuri on Ice Diputar Saat Winter Olympic Games di Pyeongchang, Korea Selatan!","content":"<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Rekaman pasangan atlit <em>figure skating </em>asal Jepang, Miu Suzaki dan Ryuichi Kihara dalam kejuaraan Winter Olympic Games di Pyeongchang kemarin jadi viral di social media. Terutama bagi penggemar anime. Tim skating dari Jepang membuat banyak orang terpukau dan terharu. Pasalnya saat lomba berlangsung, mereka menggunakan ost anime <em>Yuri On Ice </em>sebagai latar belakang musiknya.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lagu yang dipakai oleh Suzaki dan Kihara adalah lagu instrument dari opening Yuri on Ice. Sebenarnya penggunaan lagu Yuri On Ice sudah dipakai beberapa kali dalam perlombaan skating di Jepang. Tapi untuk penggunaan di perlombaan Olympic skala global, ini baru pertama kalinya. Karena itu banyak orang dan penggemar dari anime Yuri On Ice yang merasa sangat terharu melihat aksi kedua atlit yang berhasil ‘menghidupkan’ lagu tema yang dipakai pada anime.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_43325\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-43325\" data-attachment-id=\"43325\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ost-anime-yuri-ice-diputar-saat-winter-olympic-games-di-pyeongchang-korea-selatan/attachment/yuri-1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/yuri-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Getty Images&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: transforcandy.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: transforcandy.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/yuri-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/yuri-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-43325\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/yuri-1.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: transforcandy.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/yuri-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/yuri-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-43325\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: transforcandy.com</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anime Yuri On Ice pertama kali debut di TV Asahi pada Oktober 2016. Bercerita tentang Yuri Katsuki sebagai tokoh utama yang merupakan atlit figure skating yang kehilangan kepercayaan dirinya. Setelah kalah dalam perlombaan Grand Prix, Ia merasa depresi dan gak tahu harus melanjutkan mimpinya sebagai atlit atau berhenti. Suatu hari seorang atlit populer dari Rusia, Victor Nikiforov melihat potongan video Yuri yang viral di internet. Hati Victor tergerak untuk melatih Yuri, Ia pun datang ke Jepang. Dalam cerita, baik Yuri dan Victor saling membantu satu sama lain dalam meraih impian mereka sebagai seorang atlit yang harus menghadapi banyak hal: perlombaan dan persaingan yang keras.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_43326\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-43326\" data-attachment-id=\"43326\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ost-anime-yuri-ice-diputar-saat-winter-olympic-games-di-pyeongchang-korea-selatan/attachment/yuri-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/yuri-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Getty Images&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: dorkly.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: dorkly.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/yuri-2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/yuri-2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-43326\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/yuri-2.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: dorkly.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/yuri-2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/yuri-2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-43326\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: dorkly.com</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sesuai dengan lirik lagu opening dari Yuri On Ice, <em>“we were born to make history. We’ll make it happen</em>” buatan Dean Fujioka, Yuri bermimpi untuk menjadi atlit figure skating yang bisa membesarkan nama Jepang. Punya mimpi besar bukanlah hal mudah. Yuri harus melawan rasa cemas dan ragu dari dalam dirinya. Dibantu dengan teman-teman dalam tim, anime Yuri On Ice menampilkan cerita yang penuh emosional. Karena itu anime Yuri On Ice jadi salah satu anime yang sangat populer di tahun 2016-2017 dan menerima tiga penghargaan dari Tokyo Anime Award Festival. Yang membuat anime ini jadi sangat hidup dan berwarna adalah selain tampilan visual dan plot cerita, setiap adegan skating merupakan buatan seorang koreografi dan <em>ice dancer </em>pensiunan Jepang, Kenji Miyamoto.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_43329\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-43329\" data-attachment-id=\"43329\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ost-anime-yuri-ice-diputar-saat-winter-olympic-games-di-pyeongchang-korea-selatan/attachment/yuri-5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/yuri-5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Getty Images&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: wallpapermaiden.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: wallpapermaiden.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/yuri-5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/yuri-5.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-43329\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/yuri-5.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: wallpapermaiden.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/yuri-5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/yuri-5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-43329\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: wallpapermaiden.com</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_43327\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-43327\" data-attachment-id=\"43327\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ost-anime-yuri-ice-diputar-saat-winter-olympic-games-di-pyeongchang-korea-selatan/attachment/yuri-3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/yuri-3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Getty Images&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: theweek.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: theweek.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/yuri-3-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/yuri-3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-43327\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/yuri-3.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: theweek.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/yuri-3.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/yuri-3-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-43327\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: theweek.com</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Uniknya, karena anime Yuri On Ice ini populer banget <em>internationally </em>semua orang yang ikut menonton Winter Olympic Games 2018 jadi hapal dengan setiap nama gerakan yang dilakukan oleh atlit <em>figure skating!</em> Contohnya saat atlit wanita representasi Amerika, Mirai Nagasu berhasil melakukan gerakan <em>triple axel. </em>Orang-orang di Twitter langsung bilang kalau berkat anime Yuri On Ice<em>, </em>mereka jadi mengerti apa itu triple axel. Gak hanya gerakan ataupun koreografi aja, tapi juga setiap peraturan dan penilaian yang diberikan kepada atlit. Ternyata ada banyak hal yang bisa didapat dari menonton sebuah anime ya!</p>\n<p><img data-attachment-id=\"43328\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/ost-anime-yuri-ice-diputar-saat-winter-olympic-games-di-pyeongchang-korea-selatan/attachment/yuri-4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/yuri-4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;Getty Images&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: weheartit.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: weheartit.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/yuri-4-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/yuri-4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-43328 aligncenter\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/yuri-4.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: weheartit.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/yuri-4.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/yuri-4-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /></p>\n<p>Sumber: weheartit.com</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"2533e5ae-6d89-5106-8ae4-6edf9521b904"}}}